<head>RELIGION</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">宗教</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>CUSTOMARY METHOD of ACTING BASED a STANDARD of SHOULD:obligatory SACRED BELIEFS OR FAITH.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>000</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>宗教 is the modern loan translation of the Western concept.</p>
<p>教 is a traditional name for a teaching tradition.</p>
<p>道門 refers to an institutionalised intellectual tradition.</p>
<p>會門 refers to a socially organised intellectual tradition.</p>
<p>道</p>
<p>壇</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
    </div>
